						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">King: ⎯⎯ Year: 7.</hi></p>						

						<p>Damaged. Records the death of a person at Mōdanapalli when Selvagaṅgamārāyaṉ and others came and lifted cows at Mārāyappāḍi, the said person rescued the cattle but fell to an arrow and went to heaven (died).</p>						

						<p>In characters of the 13-14th century A.D.</p>						

